skins.shipDescription: Omaha-class light cruiser ¨C Omaha, Hull Number CL-4!
skins.selfIntroduction: Omaha has arrived! I was born after the first World War, but as a reconnaissance ship, I've got a lifetime's worth of intel in my brain!
skins.acquisition: Omaha-class cruiser - Omaha! Greetings, Commander! You could say that I'm a fleet veteran~! Hehe~! So, since this is the first time we meet, shouldn't you celebrate by giving me some sort of gift?
skins.login: Commander~ Any fun things you want Omaha to do today?
skins.details: M-my belly isn't fat at all, Commander! Ah, don't look at it!
skins.secretaryIdle2: You don't eat snacks, Commander? How dull your life must be!
skins.secretaryIdle3: Have you eaten yet, Commander? Cause you don't look too great...
skins.secretaryTouch: Hm... I'm getting a bit chubby? No! I'll never give up my search for the most delicious food!
skins.secretarySpecialTouch: You're not "checking if I've gained weight" at all! You're just a big old pervert, Commander~!
